name: Saruman [LotR] Mini Dude #124
description: Saruman, also known as Saruman the White was the first of the order of Istar (wizard), who came to Middle-earth as Emissaries of the Valar in the Third Age. He also was the leader of the wizards and of the White Council that opposed Sauron. [https://lotr.fandom.com/wiki/Saruman]
